{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you're interested, be sure to Wishlist the game - that helps a lot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/extras/WISHLIST_GIF.gif?t=1737402965\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/extras/panel_introduction.png?t=1737402965\" />Infinitevania is a 2D platformer in the metroidvania style, heavily inspired by Castlevania: Symphony of the Night and featuring elements from Hollow Knight. The game focuses on combat, exploration, puzzles, upgrades, and an breathtaking story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i><strong>Explore different worlds</strong></i></u> <br>Defeat the most powerful creatures in these worlds, absorb their powers, and grow stronger to destroy the core of Infinitevania and return to your own world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/extras/explore2.gif?t=1737402965\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/extras/panel_enemies.png?t=1737402965\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i><strong>Face challenging enemies</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Develop unique strategies to overcome them, adapting to each battle as you progress on your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/extras/enemies2.gif?t=1737402965\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/extras/melog2.gif?t=1737402965\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/extras/panel_puzzles_2.png?t=1737402965\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i><strong>Solve puzzles</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tackle intriguing enigmas to unlock new areas and hidden secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/extras/puzzles2.gif?t=1737402965\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/extras/panel_traps.png?t=1737402965\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i><strong>Survive deadly traps</strong></i></u> <br>Navigate treacherous environments that test your skills and reflexes at every turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/extras/traps.gif.gif?t=1737402965\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/extras/panel_upgrade.png?t=1737402965\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i><strong>Collect Upgrades to Become Stronger</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enhance your abilities and equipment throughout your adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/extras/upgrades2.gif?t=1737402965\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1983620?t=1737402965","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1983620?t=1737402965","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/52cf866dd62af27347e97256612a1bf4e97782b7/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737402965","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983620/52cf866dd62af27347e97256612a1bf4e97782b